{"tid":2135470,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特區政府強烈反對德國暫停引渡協議","createTime":"2020-08-01T12:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T13:00:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f5901d61a7c5e36472c69ff38f5e933bfbccbf5a","tid":2135470,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"特區政府指，強烈反對德國暫停同香港的引渡協議。發言人指，德國政府為了政治目的，以特區因應疫情而決定押後立法會選舉為借口，單方面暫停與香港的移交逃犯協定，是屬於雙重標準的政治操作，德國政府亦同時粗暴干涉中國内政，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。發言人批評，德國政府甘心讓犯罪分子逃避法律制裁，更凸顯了德國有機會成為一些在香港被通緝的人嘗試逃避法律責任的地方，德國要就此向法治和國際交代。 <br />\n<br />\n本港警方以違反港區國安法，通緝6名身處海外人士，包括身處德國的的本土民主前線前成員黃台仰。消息昨日傳出後，德國外長馬斯宣佈，德國將會暫停同香港的引渡協議。"},{"pid":"1f7347d727f2ee9914702ae05025d7b97034bec4","tid":2135470,"uid":239336,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L8iYB8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL8iYB8e.jpg&h=422d42f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dddb4427ceb0c75f19e8240460326fcf0d695bb5","tid":2135470,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"繼續戰狼上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe711894198e2d123e44f24ff89c1b8a004d4cd8","tid":2135470,"uid":47492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1f7347d727f2ee9914702ae05025d7b97034bec4","tid":2135470,"uid":239336,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L8iYB8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL8iYB8e.jpg&h=422d42f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"比賓狗玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973ce5fd37ccfbb1e6808fde7c9581dd8f5b8073","tid":2135470,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5901d61a7c5e36472c69ff38f5e933bfbccbf5a","tid":2135470,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score